# Directory for the macOS core logic.
#
# The USB path differs from Windows, so the contents are a separate impl.
# Expected files (add as .sh when implementing):
#   - common.sh            : shared utilities, idempotent checks, error -> next step
#   - configure-receiver.sh: send config commands to the receiver over serial
#   - run-container.sh      : docker run (passing devices) -> open the browser
#
# Once real files are added, this .gitkeep may be removed.
